// The Hermetic Qabalah

== Hermetic Qabalah
_by Oliver St. John_

=== The Tree of Life
- *The Ten Sephiroth:*
  - *Kether (1):* The Seed.
  - *Tiphereth (6):* The Gold / The Heart of the Work.
  - *Yesod (9):* The Moon / The Astral Vehicle.
  - *Malkuth (10):* The Manifested Stone / The Physical Lab.